               <p>Court. You remember Doharty's coming down to the office to speak on Burton's behalf?</p>
               <p>Macmanus. My Lord, Macdonald that belongs to the office in Litchfield-street, pointed out Doharty to me at the time, and I saw him there as plain as I see him now.</p>
               <p>Was 
               <persName id="t17830910-1-person83">
